
# Technical Architecture

## 1. System Overview
- Website built using HTML (BestWayGrow2025 repo)
- Documentation and system plan in BestWayGrow-System repo
- Modular design for easy upgrades and maintenance
- All technical modules follow BV-based activation and qualification rules defined in Design Decisions

